Maximum path step                = 100.0
Continuation Printing Frequency  = 1
------------------------------------------------------------
                 Hunting Specifications
------------------------------------------------------------
Number of hunting conditions  = -1
HC = BC 4 0    1 {speed} {2.0*speed} {0.1*speed} 0.001 100.0
HC = MT 1 1700 1 50.0 1.0 2.0 0.01 100.0
END OF HC
------------------------------------------------------------
                 Solver Specifications
------------------------------------------------------------
Solution Algorithm               = umf
Polynomial                       = LS,1
Size of Krylov subspace          = 64
Orthogonalization                = classical
Maximum Linear Solve Iterations  = 1000
Number of Newton Iterations      = 8
Newton correction factor         = 1.0 1.0 0.8 10. 0.5 100.
Normalized Residual Tolerance    = 5.0e-09
Residual Ratio Tolerance         = 1.0e-06
Linear Stability                 = no
UMF IDIM = 300000
UMF XDIM = 500000
PRESSURE DATUM                   =  0   100.0
